    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_9029989174018390070.png",
                "id": "talent20273",
                "key": "Majestic Dance",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Majestic Dance"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin <span style=\"color: #99FF88\">Dendro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/24c3fc6700c665e8f0e67239c2244d74_2721648376996397413.png",
                "id": "talent88502",
                "key": "Volatile Spore Cloud",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Volatile Spore Cloud"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 4 poin <span style=\"color: #99FF88\">Dendro DMG</span>, lalu mengonsumsi semua lapisan <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Radical Vitality</span>. Untuk setiap lapisan yang terkonsumsi, kasus ini mengakibatkan +1 DMG.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/515b825928f7e1ba52ff024f82afd1f8_4176449603895078452.png",
                "id": "talent18513",
                "key": "Feather Spreading",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Feather Spreading"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>[Pasif] Saat pertandingan dimulai, Karakter ini memperoleh <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Radical Vitality</span>. </p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/8eda35aa45e48dcada8e955719c1bfd1_3881304659641189413.png",
                "id": "talent37991",
                "key": "Radical Vitality",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Radical Vitality"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Dendro dan dapat memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bloom</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] yang memberikan +2 poin DMG ke kasus Pyro atau Electro DMG berikutnya</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, membuat [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] yang akan mengakibatkan 1 poin Pyro DMG di akhir Ronde (Jumlah penggunaan 1 kali, maksimum 2 tumpukan)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] yang memberikan +1 poin DMG ke 2 kasus Dendro DMG atau Electro DMG berikutnya</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_1674094162894706757.png",
                "id": "talent21979",
                "key": "Dendro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dendro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Radical Vitality</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status</span></p><p>Setelah Karakter ini mengakibatkan atau menerima Elemental DMG: Memperoleh 1 lapis Radical Vitality. (maksimum 3 lapis)</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Tahap Selesai</span>: Jika lapisan Radical Vitality sudah maksimum, mereka akan dihapus dan Karakter akan kehilangan semua Energy.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/03/04/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_4457584171363856773.png",
                "id": "talent44281",
                "key": "Detail Peraturan",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detail Peraturan"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
